{"lang":"ko","stage":5,"title":"everyday sentences, growing","sentences":[{"t":"여기가 어딘지 모르겠어요.","en":"I don't know where I am.","r":"yeogiga eodinji moreugesseoyo.","a":"n_10a1450640dd.mp3"},{"t":"그게 어디 있는지 모르겠어요.","en":"I don't know where it is.","r":"geuge eodi inneunji moreugesseoyo.","a":"n_88054a0655d9.mp3"},{"t":"그 사람 어디 출신이에요?","en":"Where is she from?","r":"geu saram eodi chulsini-eyo?","a":"n_a69c47fcb3ee.mp3"},{"t":"늦고 있어요.","en":"I'm running late.","r":"neutgo isseoyo.","a":"n_22b07d27c8bb.mp3"},{"t":"조금 아파요.","en":"It hurts a little.","r":"jogeum apayo.","a":"n_bd4560e68da7.mp3"},{"t":"아무 데도 안 아파요.","en":"Nothing hurts.","r":"amu dedo an apayo.","a":"n_34f04130f0f9.mp3"},{"t":"오늘은 시간이 없어요.","en":"I don't have time today.","r":"oneureun sigani eopseoyo.","a":"n_c5439109b482.mp3"},{"t":"저 여기 출신 아니에요.","en":"I'm not from here.","r":"jeo yeogi chulsin aniyeyo.","a":"n_e188b5b4e25b.mp3"},{"t":"뭘 해야 할지 모르겠어요.","en":"I don't know what to do.","r":"mwol haeya halji moreugesseoyo.","a":"n_7517609e6776.mp3"},{"t":"조금 피곤해요.","en":"I'm a little tired.","r":"jogeum pigonhaeyo.","a":"n_7e995cefcdb2.mp3"},{"t":"오늘 너무 피곤해요.","en":"I'm really tired today.","r":"oneul neomu pigonhaeyo.","a":"n_3ebf0282c6b4.mp3"},{"t":"집이 마음에 들어요.","en":"I like your house.","r":"jibi maeume deureoyo.","a":"n_6e31319af451.mp3"},{"t":"오늘은 아무것도 안 해요.","en":"Today I'm doing nothing.","r":"oneureun amugeotdo an haeyo.","a":"n_4d30d540b450.mp3"},{"t":"전부 혼자 다 해요.","en":"I do everything by myself.","r":"jeonbu honja da haeyo.","a":"n_8c4f92b05511.mp3"},{"t":"그러면 안 돼요.","en":"You don't do that.","r":"geureomyeon an dwaeyo.","a":"n_ca0fd4034c21.mp3"},{"t":"집에 가고 싶어요.","en":"I want to go home.","r":"jibe gago sipeoyo.","a":"n_67287c20831b.mp3"},{"t":"오늘 무슨 요일이에요?","en":"What day is it today?","r":"oneul museun yoiri-eyo?","a":"n_3a1e3333118c.mp3"},{"t":"커피 한 잔 사고 싶어요.","en":"I want to buy a coffee.","r":"keopi han jan sago sipeoyo.","a":"n_0d54891a1bfa.mp3"},{"t":"오늘 뭐 하고 싶어요?","en":"What do you wan